   thickness of 100 mu m (0.1 times the operation wavelength) is fabricated
   and tested with a good agreement between simulation results and
   experiments. Very exciting applications based on the presented
   structure, such as advanced angular selectivity devices with great
   rejection levels at normal incidence and angular sensing devices, can be
